## ✅ Summary

This template works for repository tests that:

- Query or filter over data sources
- Log actions or exceptions
- Normalize return types (empty instead of null)
- Are sensitive to filtering inputs

➡️ Extend this to other cases where repositories use connection factories, external APIs, or cached sources.
